&lt;p&gt;If anyone I know wants to read along on any of these, drop me a line. Love to chat about books! &amp;#x1f604;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be speculative fiction (SF, fantasy, horror with speculative elements)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Limit the number of novellas (fewer than 40k words or defined by the author as such) or combine them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A book of short stories counts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graphic novels/manga should be treated as novellas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web novels count (if they&amp;rsquo;re long enough)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audiobooks count&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
